Class SortSpec

    • Method Detail

      • getChain

        public SortSpec getChain()
        Gets the chained sort specification, or null if none. If multiple sort parameters are chained (indicating a sub-sort), the second level sort is chained via this property.

        public String getParamName()
        Returns the actual name of the search param to sort by
